    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一款结合斗地主出牌规则的肉鸽卡牌游戏，上手容易，爽感十足！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主公！组建手牌，击败各路势力（抢人妻），成为三国的霸者！这就是你的使命了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在游戏中，你将根据卡组中的牌，组成对应的牌型打出，对敌人造成伤害！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败敌人后，你就能将他们纳入麾下（后宫）啦。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>爆衣系统</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个角色都装载了爆衣系统，在游戏过程中，角色会随着关卡的推进，切换到爆衣1阶段和爆衣2阶段。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下边是部分角色的爆衣展示效果图：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/013a32430f82789aedb86f3b4bdccab3.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=649 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/013a32430f82789aedb86f3b4bdccab3.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/0afdca41fc704f452213de131610ce8e.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=649 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/0afdca41fc704f452213de131610ce8e.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/4cfa3882804c87314c47c6503439832d.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=649 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/4cfa3882804c87314c47c6503439832d.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/22e3e422ace08f3d356aa47a523c1e41.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=1327 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/22e3e422ace08f3d356aa47a523c1e41.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/e8ff2fb921928d9e48693d6d5127fe70.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=1327 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/e8ff2fb921928d9e48693d6d5127fe70.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/ab015fe8c82f3afc62d84325ab6bf79d.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=1311 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/ab015fe8c82f3afc62d84325ab6bf79d.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/749ec9989b9d358e13fb9ce21f9c2885.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=853 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/749ec9989b9d358e13fb9ce21f9c2885.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/1cac5aa956b3df091b2722f000c4d755.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=853 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/1cac5aa956b3df091b2722f000c4d755.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/f99dda3ab840849340e884eeb0050792.poster.avif?t=1761813591\" width=1170 height=894 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/f99dda3ab840849340e884eeb0050792.webm?t=1761813591\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/c9372a1a2b891b8c6329a8c3c0db3f59.avif?t=1761813591\" width=600 height=329 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/f6fecc511998ad22e3d99cf2ec30a63c.avif?t=1761813591\" width=600 height=348 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/291a74185042cdab25d23fcaf8e3e99f.avif?t=1761813591\" width=600 height=325 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/b2342282b143245473530e5900ae8e12.avif?t=1761813591\" width=600 height=383 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/ed3fd4a68061b83f7067aa16173805cd.avif?t=1761813591\" width=600 height=386 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3324350/extras/d68cbd83bed81e50c5fdb210ff638ac7.avif?t=1761813591\" width=600 height=355 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >牌型介绍：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1.单张：单张牌，比如A。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2.对子：两个点数相同的牌。比如KK。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3.连对：两个或更多连续的对子。比如3344。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4.顺子：五张或更多连续的单牌。比如34567。不包括2。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5.三张：三张点数相同的牌。比如QQQ。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6.连三张：两个或更多连续的三张。比如333444555。不包括2。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7.炸弹：四张或以上点数相同的牌。比如6666。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8.连炸弹：两个或更多连续的炸弹。比如6666677777。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击力的计算方式：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数字牌的攻击力等于牌的点数。JQK的攻击力为10，A的攻击力为11。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >组成牌型的所有牌都能造成攻击力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >实际攻击力=（组成牌型的所有牌的攻击力+牌型的默认攻击力）*牌型的攻击倍数。</p>",
